summary: Latex Mini Dress For Skyrim Womens
descriptionHtml:
Latex Mini Dress
Author: Dicekit
Version: 5.A

===============
Description:
===============

This mod adds Latex Mini Dress


1. Extract the files from the archive.
2. Copy files to (install folder)\\Skyrim
3. Start Skirim Launcher, click \'Data Files\', place a check-mark beside the Ryh Latex Dress.esp file.

===============
Un-Install:
===============

1. Start Skyrim Launcher, click Data Files, uncheck the Ryh Latex Dress.esp file.
2. Delete the files/folders associated with the mod.
